Subdivision.SubDescription: Biltmore begins with PEOPLE. Certainly, we value each homeowner that lives in a Biltmore home, but we are also referring to the valuable people that engineer our subdivisions, pave the streets for our kids to play on, pour sturdy foundations, supply the lumber, pound the nails, install our doors and market our communities. It’s hundreds of important people who make Biltmore Co. who we are. We believe in them and their strengths and we know they believe in us.

Plan.Description: The Parkside by Biltmore Co~ Great open floor plan with main level master bedroom. Large living room with access to covered patio. Kitchen features granite counters, breakfast bar and is open to the dining room. Upstairs boasts 3 bedrooms, huge family roombonus room and built~in desk.

This single level home has a kitchen that includes incredible granite counter, an island/breakfast bar, European-style alder cabinets and a large pantry. The kitchen and dining area flow right into the large great room with its gas fireplace. The lovely master suite boasts a large walk-in closet, dual vanities in the bathroom, a separate walk-in shower and a soaker tub.

We love the Messina floor plan and all that it offers growing families! Off the entry is a large office that can be closed off for work at home. The living room is spacious with a corner fireplace and opens into the wide kitchen with Bosch appliances and quartz countertops. The pocket office off the kitchen is perfect for paying bills or helping kids with school work. Enter off the garage into the dedicated mud room for easy access into the kitchen. Off the mud room is the large laundry room with a brite window looking onto the street and a door to the storage under the stairs. The owner’s bedroom on the main spans one section of the home with large picture windows and a beautiful bathroom with its large shower with dual heads and large walk in closet. The stairwell leading to upstairs is breathtaking, perfectly situated between the office and the laundry room, with wide stairs and a large picture window to flood the space with light. Bedrooms and bonus room are upstairs with well appointed large hallways, large bathrooms and lots of storage space!

Biltmore’s Fall 2012 Parade Home! 10’ ceilings throughout the main level. The dream kitchen is light and airy with beautiful cabinetry, granite counter tops and breakfast bar for seven. Home boasts theater room, office, butler’s area, formal dining and an oversized 3 car garage with RV parking. Main level master bedroom shows off the floor to ceiling windows. STUNNING!

A slightly smaller version of our “Manhattan” floorplan, our Katherine plan is the ultimate family home! Off the entry is a dedicated music/living room/office that can be doored off for privacy. The 12-foot ceiling family room is so well appointed with a full focal wall of fireplace and flanking entertainment center cabinetry. It’s open to the gorgeous kitchen with jaw dropping details and professional appliances. Our Manhattan and Katherine floor plans are known for its modern utility room design where you can enter one way into the laundry room or enter through the other side into the office/school room and they share a glass slider where you can see into each other’s space behind the kitchen. The elegant owner’s suite has dual vanities and a freestanding tub. The linen closet can be upgraded to a makeup counter. Upstairs is kid heaven with a bonus/rec room, 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Don’t miss the 21’x6’ storage room off the garage!

The Gwendolyn by Biltmore Co offers a custom blend of solidity paired with grace, qualities indicative of their building style. This floor plan offers a cozy entry patio and a two car front facing garage. A welcoming entry hallway feeds into a a spacious office, allowing workspace separate from the common areas. Enter the light filled living room and kitchen, with a dining nook perfect for entertaining family and friends. The master awaits you w/ spa inspired master bath, walk in closet & oversized windows.

The Sandalwood is a great single level floor plan with a split bed room design. Large living room that is open to the dining room and kitchen. Kitchen has granite counters, breakfast bar & huge corner pantry! Master bathroom is large and has walk-in closet, dual sinks and tile floors.

Welcome to the Silverton – a beautiful single level home by Biltmore Co. The lovely entry leads to the spacious great room, kitchen/dining areas and opens on to the covered patio and large sunroom. The kitchen features quartz counters, island/breakfast bar, alder cabinetry and a large pantry. The elegant master suite has a huge walk-in closet, separate shower, and patio access.

The Sandalwood by Biltmore Co. is a great single level floor plan with a split bedroom design, a huge upstairs bonus room that also features a fourth bedroom and full bath! Enjoy entertaining in the open and airy kitchen that boasts a center island, a breakfast bar, slab granite counters and a large pantry. The main floor master suite is large with a walk-in closet, dual sinks and tile floors. Located in beautiful Bridgetower West with a large open-space park, pond and walking paths, a community club house and pool.

“The Sawtooth” by Biltmore Co has room for everyone- 4 spacious Bedrooms including a tranquil main level master suite, bonus room, office, open great room, large kitchen that opens to the great room & a large dining area. Storage galore w/ spacious 3 car garage, oversized corner pantry, & bedrooms are complete with walk in closets.

The Spruce by Biltmore Co. Great 2 story home with a main level master bedroom. Open floor plan that flows nicely from the entry through the living room. Upstairs is open to below and boasts 3 large bedrooms & bonus area. The kitchen features breakfast bar, granite counters & hardwood floors. 9? ceilings throughout the main level. If you have never seen a Biltmore house, you need to come see this beauty!! Close to all the Meridian has to offer.

The Parkside by Biltmore Co~ Great open floor plan with main level master bedroom. Large living room with access to covered patio. Kitchen features granite counters, breakfast bar and is open to the dining room. Upstairs boasts 3 bedrooms, huge family roombonus room and built~in desk.

LIVE BIG in this 4,768 sqft bedroom dream home. This house has it all! Music/living room right off the entry, 12-foot ceiling great room, large kitchen with beautiful cabinetry storage in the dining area, Thermadore appliances and room for built in refrigerators. We love this plan because of the open access in the kitchen to the laundry room on one side and a home office on the other side. The laundry room is every woman’s dream to be able to work on one end or help the kids with home work and still have that open layout to the laundry room, full of light from the transom above. The elegant master has a freestanding tub and washer/dryer space in the closet. Upstairs is kid heaven with a 30×18 rec room. Outside don’t miss the oversized 3 car garage and the 20×8 storage room with attached mower garage with its own garage door to the back yard.
73’ Deep
Open Floor Plan

The Adalaise has plenty of curb appeal and is the perfect multi-generational home. Its style bridges modern design with elements of french and farmhouse and won all 6 first place awards in the 2019 Spring Parade of Homes, taking home Best Exterior Design, Best Master Suite, Best Kitchen, Best Decorated, Best Interior Design and Finish, and Best Overall! We love this unique floor plan because it allows for multiple places to go which is difficult to accomplish in a one-story plan. Upon entering, the 4th bedroom/office is to the left past the mud bench area with its own attached full bathroom. Upon entering to the right, is your guest wing or kids’ rooms with a full bathroom and great room and has access to the laundry room which also feeds into the master bathroom. The master bedroom is large in size and has his/hers closets including a secret closed within his closet for a safe room. The master bathroom has double vanities and a very large car wash style shower with entrances on both ends. The kitchen has beautiful views out the great room sliding doors, picture window at the dining, a task table with open shelving and an off kitchen prep area for microwave, coffee and more beautiful cabinetry.

The Hallmark plan is Kevin and Liz’s favorite floor plan as they have developed this plan over the past 20 years making it better and better each time they build it. An energy efficient two story home with an airy feeling. The 2 story great room is open to the cat walk above, making this plan so functional for families. Oversized great room features a corner gas fireplace. Large open kitchen has an island breakfast bar accommodating 4-5 barstools, cooktop, double oven and the prettiest oversized walk-in pantry. Off the entry is a large dedicated office, music room or living room with storage closet. The laundry room off the master is the perfect space for the kids to hang up their backpacks and coats. The owner’s suite is grand in size, has access to the back patio, dual vanities, separate tub, walk-in shower with 2 shower heads and a large walk-in closet. Upstairs is 4 bedrooms; 2 on each end of the house with their own bathrooms. The kids will love their own homework station near the entrance of the huge bonus room and game closet.

The Brookside – Great floor plan with master on the main level with dual sinks, walk-in shower & garden tub. Large kitchen with pantry, center island and is open to the breakfast nook & great room. Kitchen features granite, double ovens, microwave & built-in range. Formal dining room in the front, plus a study area/ office. Two bedrooms + bonus room or 3rd bedroom upstairs.

The Elizabeth is a custom designed home built to fit a specific lot with the side yard being the back yard. The side patio is covered from end to end covering the bbq area, outdoor dining and outdoor lounge. The Elizabeth’s kitchen is in-line with the dining and great room making its entertaining footprint large and open. The downstairs flow is so functional with a powder bath, lockers off the garage and an oversized laundry room. The master bedroom has his and hers separate closets with the full set of washer/dryer in hers. The upstairs bedrooms each have their own bathrooms giving this home 5 master suites. The best part of this home is the secret storage room off of the upstairs bonus room that was built into the trusses that expands above the entire downstairs great room. It’s truly a remarkable plan! The Elizabeth can be modified to fit a large lot 1/2 acre or larger.
RV Bay Garage Sq. Ftg. 1685
Open Floor Plan
Laundry Room With A View Upstairs
Open Floor Plan

The Weston-Spectacular home with Great room, den and bonus room. Gourmet kitchen boasts full tile backsplash, breakfast bar, dishwasher, double oven, pantry, island, alder cabinets & quartz countertops. Tile and hardwood flooring. Tech room off kitchen. Set up for central vacuum. Energy efficient. Full automatic sprinklers. This gorgeous home has great attention to detail. You’ll love every inch!!!
Covered Porch

This is an elegantly-designed home with high-end finishes. The gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances, European-style alder cabinets, a huge pantry, a built-in double oven, full tile backsplash and hardwood floors. The owner’s suite boasts a tray ceiling, the gorgeous tiled bathroom and a spacious closet. This home includes a spacious ensuite/4th bedroom with a private bath and walk-in closet. Upstairs you will find the bonus room with its closet and full bath.
Open Floor Plan

“The Sawtooth” by Biltmore Co has room for everyone- 4 spacious Bedrooms including a tranquil main level master suite, bonus room, office, open great room, large kitchen that opens to the great room & a large dining area. Storage galore w/ spacious 3 car garage, oversized corner pantry, & bedrooms are complete with walk in closets.
Open Floor Plan
Laundry Room With A View Upstairs

The Stratton is your family’s next new home! Our 2018 Spring Parade Home won 3 awards this year in the areas of Best Master Suite, Best Kitchen and Best Overall! This strapping modern, urban, craftsman has vaulted ceilings in almost every room of the house, 2 story wrap-around staircase, fireplace in the Kitchen Hearth Room, large bonus room, kids computer space, beams and hardwood floors through all main-level living areas. Striking tiled kitchen hood, large pantry & black stainless appliances. The master suite is your retreat with his/hers vanities, double mirrored wood closet doors and a stand-alone soaker tub.

Beautiful 2 story home with all the bedrooms upstairs plus a laundry room. This home features a spacious living room that is open to the kitchen and dining area. The kitchen features gorgeous granite counter tops and a large pantry. Upstairs you’ll find all four bedrooms. The master bedroom includes dual vanities and a spacious walk in closet.
2892 sq. ft.

The Baby Katherine By Biltmore Co. has everything you want and more? This beautiful home’s floor plan includes a flex room, main floor master suite, gorgeous kitchen with jaw dropping details and Bosch appliances. Upstairs is a huge family room and 3 bedrooms. This elegant home also features an over-sized modern utility room and a large storage room off the 3-car garage.

“The Sassafrass”-This single level craftsman style home is designed with Energy Star in mind. Spacious floor plan that includes 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Large master bedroom and master bath with dual sinks, walk-ins shower plus soaking tub. Built in desk for all your special projects. Large Great Room with access to the back yard. Biltmore’s signature custom molding throughout. Spacious laundry room with shelving & counter space. Hardwood floors throughout the dining, kitchen & halls. Great floor plan!
Bonus Room Upstairs

This sprawling floor plan hits all the buttons in this modern 1 story floor plan. The kitchen is a dream with a possible hidden pantry behind a cabinet door, large island, cooktop, double ovens & quartz counters. Room off of the entry can be a dedicated office or dining room. Great room with beautiful gas fireplace flows off the kitchen. Divine Master bedroom has large picture windows, a stunning open master retreat with free standing tub and a large closet even she will love! Enjoy the door out the master to the covered patio. This home can be designed with a full 2nd master suite. The flex room at the end of the hall is in the perfect location, ready for the kids to play in or watch movies.
Open Floor Plan

Welcome to the Spyglass! This beautiful, single-level home by Biltmore Co. features a covered front porch, over-sized covered patio extending the entire width of the home and a 3 car garage. You’ll love the free-flowing floor plan that has plenty of room for everyone with a magnificent great room with fireplace and built-in entertainment center cabinets, extra large kitchen, large flex room behind the kitchen and a dedicated office area. The master suite has dual vanities, a huge walk-in closet and private access to the patio.

This 2016 Parade of Home has a soaring 2 story entry and downstairs hallways. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, space for a second commercial-grade refrigerator inside the pantry and the dining area can be set up for a large banquet. The floor plan boasts two master suites, an amazing laundry/craft/office room, a built-in kid’s reading bunk under the stairs {or storage}, a gas-lit real wood-burning stove in the great room, and an upstairs loft, bonus room, bedroom and full bath. Don’t forget the garage where there are multiple garage storage areas, a separate mower garage and lots of covered patio space.
